snippet.title: Mosh Pit Simulator Actual Trailer
snippet.description:
Mosh Pit Simulator coming to Steam Early Access on January 31, 2019!

Check it out on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/486440/Mosh_Pit_Simulator/
Visit the website: http://moshpitsimulator.com/
Join Discord: https://discord.gg/zV3WNeP

Mosh Pit Simulator is an open-world physical sand-box game about a world that is overrun by brainless boneless humanoid creatures due to a terrible accident. It's going to be available for HTC Vive, Oculus Rift with Touch controllers and Windows MR devices pretty soon!
